{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Device Orientation Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>這是一個實驗中的功能</strong><br>此功能在某些瀏覽器尚在開發中，請參考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">兼容表格</a>以得到不同瀏覽器用的前輟。</p></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code> 提供了網頁開發者關於裝置位置及旋轉方向改變時的速度資訊。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>警告：</strong> Currently, Firefox and Chrome does not handle the coordinates the same way. Take care about this while using them.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.acceleration_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An object giving the acceleration of the device on the three axis X, Y and Z. Acceleration is expressed in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.accelerationincludinggravity_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An object giving the acceleration of the device on the three axis X, Y and Z with the effect of gravity. Acceleration is expressed in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.rotationrate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An object giving the rate of change of the device's orientation on the three orientation axis alpha, beta and gamma. Rotation rate is express in degrees per seconds.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.interval_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A number representing the interval of time, in milliseconds, at which data is obtained from the device.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'devicemotion'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>acceleration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' m/s2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/#devicemotion","title":"DeviceOrientation Event Specification"}],"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Detecting_device_orientation\">Detecting device orientation</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\">Orientation and motion data explained</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"DeviceMotionEvent 提供了網頁開發者關於裝置位置及旋轉方向改變時的速度資訊。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/devicemotionevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/devicemotionevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","title":"DeviceMotionEvent"}],"pageTitle":"DeviceMotionEvent - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}